author: Disney
description:
D23 Members are invited to join for a frightfully festive celebration in the D23 Gold Theater presented by State Farm with “Making Haunted Mansion Holiday with Don Hahn.” 

Join Disney Legend Don Hahn as he guides you through the spellbinding story of how the Haunted Mansion becomes a Nightmare Before Christmas wonderland in just two short weeks. Enjoy special appearances from Danny Elfman, Henry Selick, Imagineers, Archivists, and more!

Tune in for the latest installment of D23 Gold Theater at https://theater.d23.com/ on Thursday, October 23, 2025, exclusively for Gold Members with an encore offering for all D23 Members on Thursday, October 30, 2025.

Not a D23 Gold Member? Become one today https://d23.com/join/

author: Disney
description:
Royal sisters on a mission! ❄️🏰 Go on an all-new adventure in LEGO Disney Frozen: Operation Puffins, an original special available October 24 only on Disney+.  

After the events of Frozen, Anna and Elsa want to start fresh in Arendelle, and make the castle feel a bit more comfortable. While they struggle to break free of the bounds of tradition, the Duke of Weselton has other plans for their beloved home alongside a flock of menacing puffins. LEGO Disney Frozen: Operation Puffins available only on Disney+ October 24.
